%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 6fd7c7e213ea3424784e4d44afe4baba, type: 3}
  m_Name: SpringDay1_HouseArrival
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  sequenceId: spring-day1-house-arrival
  nodes:
  - speakerName: 村长
    text: 先在这边站稳。围观的人虽然散开了，可今晚还没人真把你算成自己人。
    isGarbled: 0
    garbledText:
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    isInnerMonologue: 0
    isBubble: 0
    fontStyleKey: default
    typingSpeedOverride: 0
  - speakerName: ""
    text: （村口那股注视只是退远了一点，没有真正散干净。这里先给了我一条路，却还没把我接成自己人。）
    isGarbled: 0
    garbledText:
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    isInnerMonologue: 1
    isBubble: 0
    fontStyleKey: narration
    typingSpeedOverride: 0
  - speakerName: 旅人
    text: 这里……至少比矿洞口像活人该站的地方。谢谢你先把我带到这里。
    isGarbled: 0
    garbledText:
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    isInnerMonologue: 0
    isBubble: 0
    fontStyleKey: default
    typingSpeedOverride: 0
  - speakerName: 村长
    text: 我不是把你完全收进村子了，只是先给你一口喘气的地方。今晚别乱走，先把命稳下来。
    isGarbled: 0
    garbledText:
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    isInnerMonologue: 0
    isBubble: 0
    fontStyleKey: default
    typingSpeedOverride: 0
  - speakerName: 村长
    text: 艾拉就在这附近。先让她把你的伤压住，别的事等天亮再说。
    isGarbled: 0
    garbledText:
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    isInnerMonologue: 0
    isBubble: 0
    fontStyleKey: default
    typingSpeedOverride: 0
  - speakerName: 旅人
    text: 今晚先给我一个落脚处，明天再决定要不要继续留我……是这个意思吧。
    isGarbled: 0
    garbledText:
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    isInnerMonologue: 0
    isBubble: 0
    fontStyleKey: default
    typingSpeedOverride: 0
  - speakerName: ""
    text: （村里的光和人声都还在不远处，我像是终于从矿洞口那边被拉回了活人的地方。）
    isGarbled: 0
    garbledText:
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    isInnerMonologue: 1
    isBubble: 0
    fontStyleKey: narration
    typingSpeedOverride: 0
  canSkip: 1
  defaultTypingSpeed: 45
  markLanguageDecodedOnComplete: 0
  advanceStoryPhaseOnComplete: 0
  nextStoryPhase: 0
  followupSequence: {fileID: 0}
